Additional information: For Visitors and Working Holiday Makers the processing time is calculated differently depending on when you applied. If you applied before the border reopened, then the processing time is calculated from the date you became eligible to travel. If you applied after the border reopened, then the processing time is calculated from the date you applied.​

Currently, the Department is prioritising applications on the Priority Migration Skilled Occupation List (PMSOL), those in critical sectors as per Ministerial Directions and for applicants outside Australia. In August 2022, 50 per cent of applications where the client is outside Australia were finalised in 66 days.
